710786f-b.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 50th Street
710786f-b.text:
Twelfth Avenue, west side, north from W1.50th Street, showing the piers
lining the waterfront. View 1 is at 50th Street and view 2 north from
53rd Street. Piles of gravel are shown on the left.
P.L.Sperr  View 1:April 14, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2:March 20, 1927

710789f-b.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 50th Street
710789f-b.text:
Twelfth Avenue, east side, north from West 50th Street.
showing the new frontage of this thoroughfare after a
slice was removed from this side. The building with the
sign '' Rims - Wheels'' faces on the north side of 51st
Street. The small cottage is No. 634 West 52nd Street.
April 15, 1934
March 26, 1935
P. L. Sperr
NO REPREODUCTIONS
